This is a Python CLI project for exploring TransformerLens model behavior.

Do not make broad refactors unless explicitly asked.

Prefer small, reviewable changes.

Before editing code:
- explain the intended change
- identify the files that will be touched
- wait for approval unless the task is trivial

Project conventions:
- YAML stores metadata and summaries only
- raw tensors belong in separate .pt files
- snapshot creation and comparison logic should remain separated
- avoid dumping large tensor lists into YAML

Use existing tests when available.
If no tests exist, suggest a small test before changing behavior.
